nodes.text: A male market stand owner was present on Coruscant around 21 BBY during the time of the Clone Wars.

This vendor owned a stand in the planet Coruscant's lower market districts. When Assassin droid HELIOS-3D was sent by Cad Bane to snatch Astromech droid R2-D2, the latter used his suction cup cable on this vendor's stand and pulled it down in front of the pursuers in an attempt to slow them down.
This owner belonged to the same species as Rang Thang and was voiced by Terrence Carson.
